HEADWORD: Urosternite
<hw>U`ro*ster"nite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[2d
<ets>uro-</ets> + <ets>sternum</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The
sternal, or under piece, of any one of the uromeres of insects and other
arthropods.</def>⟦br⟧
